skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: venice skater guide
des:
Venice Skater Guide is the perfect Venice Skatepark companion. It gives a short bio on some of the best skateboarders at the Venice Skatepark. Ask Alexa to find skateboarders from Venice and it will give you a list of skaters to pick from. Once you have info on a particular skater, you can ask for more info and it will give more info and a photo of the skater. Alexa will also offer to give information on random skaters.
Not all the skaters are from Venice. But it’s a good starting point.
Venice Skater Guide lets you ask questions like “Find me skaters from Venice”, or “What is Haden’s instagram username?” , or “Tell me about Matt LeMond?”.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
